name: Fattie and a diet
description:
Fattie is a Cat, who from time to time has to keep on a diet. While keeping on a diet, Fattie eats healthy food and sometimes plays with it like he is playing with a banana now. Please, do not worry if he loses some weight. More weight he loses, more food he can eat after, fewer hungry cats in the World. 

50% of the proceeds raised with this kitty will be used to improve the lives of cats around the world.
